title: He-Man and the Masters of the Universe 001-016 (2013-Ongoing)
description:
He-Man and the Masters of the Universe 2013-Ongoing

I take no credit for this other than I collected them for everyone to obtain easier than looking for individual issues (like I had to).  All credit goes to the original scanners/uploaders.



Description:

Whenever Prince Adam holds his Power Sword aloft and says the magic words "By the Power of Grayskull, I HAVE THE POWER" he is transformed into He-Man, the most powerful man in the universe. Together with his close allies, The Masters of the Universe, He-Man uses his powers to defend Eternia from evil.
